.4]}, {"text": "Employee Retirement Income Security Act of 1974. We also sponsor a deferred profit sharing plan for the", "bbox": [143.8, 1012.5, 1094.1, 1033.4]}, {"text": "benefit of the full-time employees of our Canadian subsidiaries. Under these plans, we match a percentage of the", "bbox": [143.8, 1037.5, 1094.1, 1058.4]}, {"text": "participants’ contributions up to a specified amount. Company contributions to the plans were $26, $23 and $22", "bbox": [143.8, 1062.6, 1094.2, 1083.4]}, {"text": "in the years ended December 31, 2017, 2016 and 2015, respectively.", "bbox": [143.8, 1087.6, 714.9, 1108.4]}, {"text": "Environmental Matters", "bbox": [143.8, 1141.4, 354.0, 1162.3]}, {"text": "The Company and its operations are subject to various laws and related regulations governing", "bbox": [185.5, 1176.3, 1094.1, 1197.2]}, {"text": "environmental matters. Under such laws, an owner or lessee of real estate may be liable for the costs of removal", "bbox": [143.8, 1201.3, 1094.0, 1222.2]}, {"text": "or remediation of certain hazardous or toxic substances located on or in, or emanating from, such property, as", "bbox": [143.8, 1226.4, 1094.2, 1247.2]}, {"text": "well as investigation of property damage. We incur ongoing expenses associated with the performance of", "bbox": [143.8, 1251.4, 1094.2, 1272.2]}, {"text": "appropriate remediation at certain locations.", "bbox": [143.8, 1276.4, 512.1, 1297.2]}, {"text": "15.", "bbox": [143.8, 1330.2, 169.9, 1351.1]}, {"text": "Common Stock", "bbox": [190.7, 1330.2, 327.9, 1351.1]}, {"text": "We have 500 million authorized shares of common stock, $0.01 par value. At December 31, 2017 and 2016,", "bbox": [185.5, 1365.2, 1094.2, 1386.0]}, {"text": "there were 0.5 million shares of common stock reserved for issuance pursuant to options granted under our stock", "bbox": [143.8, 1390.2, 1094.1, 1411.0]}, {"text": "option plans.", "bbox": [143.8, 1415.2, 251.6, 1436.0]}, {"text": "91", "bbox": [608.6, 1465.8, 629.4, 1486.6]}]}